buyerAgent.name: Your Home Sold Guaranteed Realty - Kings of Real Estate Team

data.description: Awesome, move-in ready home located in the heart of Loudon, just 7min from the interstate!! This single level, split floor plan home features hardwood/tiled floors throughout, a great kitchen island w/ built-in bar seating, numerous windows for plenty of natural lighting, spacious primary suite w/ walk-in closet, huge attached 2-car garage and more! Outside you'll find a cleared level lot, covered front porch, and a massive back deck located within a privacy fenced yard!! Only minutes from local grocery stores/schools and a short drive to Knoxville, you can enjoy all of this with NO HOA DUES and low property taxes!!!
